    h2 Why
    br
    p This template arose out of a need to unite all the above libraries, which were not found in the existing Vite templates. This template has an active contributors that will update everything on this template as needed
    br
    h2 Usage
    br
    p If you are using either Yarn or NPM run the command bellow
    code
        lang bash
        + npx degit potreco/viterc my-app
        +
        + cd my-app
        +
        + # Required if you want a repository and work with Git hooks
        + git init
        +
        + yarn install
        +
        + yarn dev
    br
    p If you are using Bun
    code
        lang bash
        + bun create potreco/viterc/bun my-app
        +
        + cd my-app
        +
        + # Required if you want a repository and work with Git hooks
        + git init
        +
        + bun install
        +
        + bun run dev
    br
